             was indicted for <rs id="t18200918-256-off1467" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200918-256-off1467" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200918-256-off1467" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200918-256-cd1468" type="crimeDate">19th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-256-off1467 t18200918-256-cd1468"></join>, one watch, value 2 l., and one key, value 2 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-256-victim2405" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Carr
                        <interp inst="t18200918-256-victim2405" type="surname" value="Carr"></interp>
